            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I'm pretty confident that, for most people, this is as much video editing power as they need. Certainly, if you're not a pro doing three social videos a day, every day, this is more than enough for you. ",
